<br>
As for concussion.  If your looking at what spells are cast and counting them, I sure wouldn't want to be in your group.. I especially wouldn't want the tank cause it shows how much attention your paying to them!! I know I said Wizards w/out Concussion are crazy.. but I didn't say they were stupid.<br>
